Take the sentence as input, align justified left align, right align
program:

def justify_text(sentence, width=50):
    left_aligned = sentence.ljust(width)
    right_aligned = sentence.rjust(width)
    return left_aligned, right_aligned

input_sentence = input("Enter a sentence: ")
left, right = justify_text(input_sentence)

print("Left Aligned:\n", left)
print("Right Aligned:\n", right)

Output:
Enter a sentence:  lahari venkatesh yegi
Left Aligned:
 lahari yegi                                          
Right Aligned:
                                            lahari yegi
